      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey so im getting a MemoryError when i try to process this massive csv file in pandas. i think it might be because im loading the whole thing at once. what is the actual difference between using a list comprehension vs a generator in terms of how much RAM they use? i need to keep the memory footprint low.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
